            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Wow, this is something I have been dreaming of for too many years to count!\n\nI have been playing a bit with the examples, and trying to figure out how this works. Is there any way in Lopecode to search for references to specific cells? For example, I have been wondering how the \"robotEditor\" cell actually contributes to the animation, as I haven't seen it referenced so far."
